柘.definition: a thorny tree; sugarcane; Cudrania triloba; three-bristle cudrania (Cudrania tricuspidata); Chinese mulberry (Cudrania)

柘城縣.definition: Zhecheng county in Shangqiu 商丘[Shang1 qiu1], Henan

柘弓.definition: bow made from the 柘[zhe4] tree

柘彈.definition: slingshot made from the 柘[zhe4] tree

柘榮.definition: Zherong county in Ningde 寧德|宁德[Ning2 de2], Fujian

柘榮縣.definition: Zherong county in Ningde 寧德|宁德[Ning2 de2], Fujian

柘硯.definition: ink slabs from a place in Shandong

柘絲.definition: silk from worms fed on 柘[zhe4] leaves

柘黃.definition: yellow dye made from the bark of the 柘[zhe4] tree
